body_html: I had similar problem with Dequantization Kernel not being register when trying to execute inception V3 in 8bit mode. I fixed it in the bazel script under the target and included the quantization operators as dependencies. The kernel registrations should happen as file globals (I believe) so it looks like there is a disconnect with the "Sub" operator and the dependencies in bazel for that particular target.
